# Local-loop dev-only vars/secrets (wrangler dev loads this file; production never sees it).
#
# DEV_APP_ORIGIN is intentionally NOT set here — the npm scripts provide it via `--var`, so it stays
# the single switch for where the local site reads data (SSR fetches + app-host redirects + the
# client viewer, via window.SM_API_BASE injected by the Worker):
#   npm run dev         → http://localhost:8788      (local app Worker + local D1)
#   npm run dev:remote  → https://app.smplmark.org   (production data, no ?api= needed)
#
# Add any real dev-only secrets below.
